flowRoot.flowPara: 1- Stacked cross-validated predictions from each modal data in the training set fit a LASSO estimator.
2- Stacked predictions from each modal data in the test set used for final prediction.
1- 5-Fold cross-validation yields out-of-sample predictions in each independent piece of data in the training set.
2 - Fitted LASSO-PCR regressors yield predictions for each independent data in the test set.
